summary: au idea I got: YA GIRL NEEDS THOUGHTS (I have two days left of school and I'm losing my mind)
body:
au idea I got: YA GIRL NEEDS THOUGHTS (I have two days left of school and I’m losing my mind)

Hello beautiful human being reading this- I haven’t watched Andi Mack in literal months but at two in the morning I came up with an AU idea where Cyrus works at a coffee shop and TJ goes there every morning to order an obnoxious drink to get on Cy’s nerves; to get back at Teej Cyrus always writes a random thing of what TJ could stand for but the two turn it into a game when TJ says he’ll go out with Cyrus when Cyrus figures out what TJ stands for

It’s tooth rotting fluff but it’ll be sm fun to write

Is this a stupid idea??? Probably, but that’s why I’m asking all of y'all yEET

I have two days of school left finals are draining me

Here’s an excerpt, could you tell me if it sounds okay or not?

—

“So, what would you recommend? I’ve never been much of a coffee guy,” The boy with the fading purple hair who’s name tag says Cyrus laughs.

“You could get a vanilla frap, there isn’t coffee in that,”

“Sure, why not. Does it have caffeine?” He shakes his head as he starts to write on the cup.

“No, but I can put some espresso shots in it to wake you up if you need them…what’s your name?” He looks up at me with those dark brown eyes inquisitively, leaning across the counter so our faces are only a few inches apart.

“Um, TJ,”

A brunette haired boy grabs him by the elbow and pulls him away from me before muttering to him, “Cy, stop flirting with the customers,”

Cyrus giggles, ruffling the brunette’s hair. “Sorry, Jonah. Would it make you feel better if I promised not to do it again?” He juts out his bottom lip at the other boy. “What, is it making you jealous?”

Jonah goes bright red as he sticks his tongue out at Cyrus and goes back to making the drink for a short haired girl sitting in the corner of the room.

—

Thoughts??? Please let me know what you think lovelies!
